  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >STORY</h2><br>A mysterious group of cultists is protecting a creature from beyond who wants nothing but chaos.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >KEY FEATURES</h2><br>KARM is a fast-paced retro FPS inspired by the look and feel of the early 90's classics. <br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>EXPLORE</strong> 30 abstract labyrinthian maps full of secrets in a lovecraftian world.<br></li><li><strong>MOVE</strong> fast, <strong>DODGE</strong> projectiles and <strong>SHOOT</strong> at 8 different enemies and 3 bosses with 7 unique weapons.<br></li><li><strong>CUSTOMIZE</strong> your HUD and some other features to suit your play style.</li></ul><br><strong>FORGET</strong> bunny hopping and reloading, <strong>LISTEN</strong> to the badass music and <strong>KILL'EM ALL</strong>!",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >STORY</h2><br>A mysterious group of cultists is protecting a creature from beyond who wants nothing but chaos.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >KEY FEATURES</h2><br>KARM is a fast-paced retro FPS inspired by the look and feel of the early 90's classics. <br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>EXPLORE</strong> 30 abstract labyrinthian maps full of secrets in a lovecraftian world.<br></li><li><strong>MOVE</strong> fast, <strong>DODGE</strong> projectiles and <strong>SHOOT</strong> at 8 different enemies and 3 bosses with 7 unique weapons.<br></li><li><strong>CUSTOMIZE</strong> your HUD and some other features to suit your play style.</li></ul><br><strong>FORGET</strong> bunny hopping and reloading, <strong>LISTEN</strong> to the badass music and <strong>KILL'EM ALL</strong>!",
